# Title: PowerShell ShellCode
# Author: David Ledbetter (shellcode), Florian Roth (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2018-11-17
# Level: high
# Description: Detects Base64 encoded Shellcode
# MITRE Tactic: Defense Evasion
# Tags: attack.defense-evasion, attack.privilege-escalation, attack.t1055, attack.execution, attack.t1059.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/powershell/powershell_script/posh_ps_shellcode_b64.yml

ScriptBlockText IN ("*OiCAAAAYInlM*", "*OiJAAAAYInlM*")